== 传记 ==

约翰娜·叔本华（婚前姓Trosiener）生于[[格但斯克|但泽]]。她成为一名作家并描写她在本城的生活。在1793年她的城市被[[普鲁士王国|普鲁士]]吞并後，她和她的丈夫搬到了[[汉堡|汉堡]]。在1807年她的丈夫死后，她又搬到了[[魏玛|魏玛]]。<!--and belonged to the literary circle surrounding [[Johann_Wolfgang_von_Goethe|Johann Wolfgang von Goethe]].  The charming coffee shop where she "held court" with authors and intellectuals of her day still stands in front of a statue of Goethe by the opera house square in modern Weimar. When told by Goethe that her son was destined for great things, she objected, claiming that there could not be ''two'' geniuses in one family.-->

